\c 131 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 131\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Gad Of Deebisanii Waaqayyotti Of Kennachuu (Weedduu ittiin ol ba'an; kan Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, garaan koo waan guddaatti of hin ilaalu, mataa irra-keessa qabadhee hin adeemu; wanta anatti guddatee, humna koo gararraattis dinqisiisaa ta'e keessa hin lixu.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ani lubbuu koo urursee cal jechisiiseera; akkuma mucaan erga harma gu'ee iyyuu haadha isaa yommuu argatu calluma jedhu, lubbuun koos isa argattetti calluma in jetti.
\m \bd 3\bd* Yaa Israa'el, ammaa jalqabee hamma bara baraatti, Waaqayyoon abdiidhaan eeggadhu!
\b 
